  "elapsed_s": 116.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Some of these pieces-- by the way, one piece in particular-- it is called 'Crematorium'-- is extraordinary powerfully written piece of music that is enable you almost to live through the experience of the Jewish people inside of the chamber [INAUDIBLE] gas, almost to hear the screams and agony, to hear the prayers of the, the children.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This is a piece written in a very contemporary style and [INAUDIBLE] style.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's almost prophetic because it was written before that, the, the, some of these executions happened.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 'Agony'-- this is the subtitle of this pieces, piece, 'Agony,' written by one of the brilliant disciples of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Schoenberg.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I wish that there is little bit time that you'd be able to hear some of this piece.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then this will illustrate it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It'll be stronger words that I'm trying now to describe the music.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And music is very difficult to describe through words.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's necessary to experience the, the music itself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So let's leave the music to speak by itself--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--through these few pieces that I prepared for violin alone, violin solo.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're very welcome.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The piece of music that you'll be hearing now is part of my collection Lost Voices.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that is, is containing music by composers that perished during the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some of the music that those people wrote is almost prophetic in character and merits to take part of the Jewish heritage, not only by the merits of the fact that it's composed by martyrs of the Jewish history by proper, properly-- simply because of the value of the music itself.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The piece that now you'll be hearing is call 'In Memoriam' and is written by Ben Susam, Menachem Ben Susam.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
